@startuml
title Flow F-003: Document upload

actor Client
participant "Document API" as DocumentAPI
participant "Validation Boundary" as ValidationBoundary
participant "Authorization Policy" as AuthorizationPolicy
participant "Filesystem Adapter" as FilesystemAdapter
participant "Metadata Repository" as MetadataRepository
participant "Audit Service" as AuditService

Client -> DocumentAPI: Upload document request
DocumentAPI -> ValidationBoundary: Validate size + metadata
ValidationBoundary --> DocumentAPI: Valid request
DocumentAPI -> AuthorizationPolicy: Validate upload scope
AuthorizationPolicy --> DocumentAPI: Authorized
DocumentAPI -> FilesystemAdapter: Store content safely
FilesystemAdapter --> DocumentAPI: Stored reference
DocumentAPI -> MetadataRepository: Persist metadata
DocumentAPI -> AuditService: Persist audit event
DocumentAPI --> Client: Upload result
@enduml
